### Get all players
GET http://localhost:8080/players
Accept: application/json

###

### Get player by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/players/{id}
Accept: application/json

###

### Add a new player
POST http://localhost:8080/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "gender": "Male",
  "country": "USA",
  "birthdate": "1990-01-01",
  "location": "New York",
  "fencingWeapon": "Foil",
  "bio": "Experienced fencer.",
  "wins": 10,
  "losses": 5,
  "points": 100,
  "ranking": 3
}

###

### Update a player's details (ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/players/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "gender": "Male",
  "country": "USA",
  "birthdate": "1990-01-01",
  "location": "Los Angeles",
  "fencingWeapon": "Epee",
  "bio": "Champion fencer.",
  "wins": 15,
  "losses": 3,
  "points": 120,
  "ranking": 1
}

###

### Delete a player (ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/players/{id}
Accept: application/json

###

### Edit a player's details (for USERS)
PUT http://localhost:8080/players/{id}/edit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "gender": "Male",
  "country": "USA",
